{"tid":683014,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"HPV Coffee 都有人埋單   真係娛樂性工作者嘅勵志故事","createTime":"2018-05-29T10:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T13:25:18.000Z","uid":159734,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"82c8e0438fd5f7c5ed056f3add2ac219907becf0","tid":683014,"uid":159734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"以前就話娶妻求淑女，估唔到而家d 人鍾意娶妻求肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條女係殘廁都比人攪得，又比江湖大佬包養，男友車輪轉咁濟，慌死人唔知佢日夜被人抽插咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條仔搵到錢又做銀行高層咁都要條淫婦埋單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n所以話係香港地，只要你身材好，就算做雞做到出哂面都唔怕，埋單條隊一樣大排長龍<br />\n<br />\n如果咁多位巴打唔記得咗Valarie Lam 嘅豐富情史，不妨重溫一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/183811_cc487b3af4cd0ebbc3abe495d1b0fd85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F183811_cc487b3af4cd0ebbc3abe495d1b0fd85.png&h=5550275a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/183854_29ecbca65e9f431c5131a5e163abaadc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F183854_29ecbca65e9f431c5131a5e163abaadc.png&h=5116f6e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/183910_2fd5db7fda1077c18a69180cb647b7cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F183910_2fd5db7fda1077c18a69180cb647b7cc.png&h=879c7465&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/183928_06e92b28146889313556e2bee986b745.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F183928_06e92b28146889313556e2bee986b745.png&h=f9662463&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"htt